            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3EEzekiel%2040%3A28-41%3A26%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_28%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2228%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EGateways%20to%20the%20Inner%20Courtyard%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E28%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20the%20man%20took%20me%20to%20the%20south%20gateway%20leading%20into%20the%20inner%20courtyard.%20He%20measured%20it%2C%20and%20it%20had%20the%20same%20measurements%20as%20the%20other%20gateways.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_29%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E29%3C%2Fspan%3EIts%20guard%20alcoves%2C%20dividing%20walls%2C%20and%20entry%20room%20were%20the%20same%20size%20as%20those%20in%20the%20others.%20It%20also%20had%20windows%20along%20its%20walls%20and%20in%20the%20entry%20room.%20And%20like%20the%20others%2C%20the%20gateway%20passage%20was%2087%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%20long%20and%2043%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%20wide.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_30%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2230%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E30%3C%2Fspan%3E(The%20entry%20rooms%20of%20the%20gateways%20leading%20into%20the%20inner%20courtyard%20were%2014%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E40%3A30%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%2040%3A9%2C%20which%20reads%20%3Cem%3E8%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%3C%2Fem%3E%20%5B14%26%23xA0%3Bfeet%20or%204.2%26%23xA0%3Bmeters%5D%3B%20here%20the%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3E5%26%23xA0%3Bcubits%3C%2F