%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%20wide.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_34%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2234%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E34%3C%2Fspan%3EIts%20entry%20room%20faced%20into%20the%20outer%20courtyard.%20It%20had%20palm%20tree%20decorations%20on%20its%20columns%2C%20and%20there%20were%20eight%20steps%20leading%20to%20its%20entrance.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_35%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2235%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E35%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20he%20took%20me%20around%20to%20the%20north%20gateway%20leading%20to%20the%20inner%20courtyard.%20He%20measured%20it%2C%20and%20it%20had%20the%20same%20measurements%20as%20the%20other%20gateways.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_36%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2236%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E36%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20guard%20alcoves%2C%20dividing%20walls%2C%20and%20entry%20room%20of%20this%20gateway%20had%20the%20same%20measurements%20as%20in%20the%20others%20and%20the%20same%20window%20arrangements.%20The%20gateway%20passage%20measured%2087%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%20long%20and%2043%3Csup%20class%3D%22fract-num%22%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-slash%22%3E%2F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22fract-den%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3E%20feet%20wide.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_37%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2237%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E37%3C%2Fspan%3EIts%20entry%20room%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E40%3A37%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%20(compare%20parallels%20at%2040%3A26%2C%2031%2C%2034)%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3EIts%20dividing%20wall.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20faced%20into%20the%20outer%20courtyard%2C%20and%20it%20had%20palm%20tree%20decorations%20on%20the%20columns.%20There%20were%20eight%20steps%20leading%20to%20its%20entrance.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_38%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2238%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3ERooms%20for%20Preparing%20Sacrifices%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E38%3C%2Fspan%3EA%20door%20led%20from%20the%20entry%20room%20of%20one%20of%20the%20inner%20gateways%20into%20a%20side%20room%2C%20where%20the%20meat%20for%20sacrifices%20was%20washed.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_39%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2239%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E39%3C%2Fspan%3EOn%20each%20side%20of%20this%20entry%20room%20were%20two%20tables%2C%20where%20the%20sacrificial%20animals%20were%20slaughtered%20for%20the%20burnt%20offerings%2C%20sin%20offerings%2C%20and%20guilt%20offerings.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_40%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2240%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E40%3C%2Fspan%3EOutside%20the%20entry%20room%2C%20on%20each%20side%20of%20the%20stairs%20going%20up%20to%20the%20north%20entrance%2C%20were%20two%20more%20tables.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_41%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2241%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E41%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20there%20were%20eight%20tables%20in%20all%26%23x2014%3Bfour%20inside%20and%20four%20outside%26%23x2014%3Bwhere%20the%20sacrifices%20were%20cut%20up%20and%20prepared.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22ezek_40_42%22%20bk%3D%22ezek%22%20ch%3D%2240%22%20vn%3D%2242%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E42%3C%2Fspan%3EThere%20were%20also%20four%20tables%20of%20finished%20stone%20for%20preparation%20of%20the%20burnt%20offerings%2C%20each%2031%3Csup%20class%